name: Kiki - By the sea

reviews.review_text:
Positive things first - the vibe of the place is just really soft and soothing, a perfect place for your family to hangout and have a couple of cocktails. We loved the vibe with really good crowd. It’s in the backwaters so you can experience a really warm breeze coming in instead of sea smell which could be irritating sometimes. The location was perfect in a way to have a good time with your family and friends. Even the food was not that bad. The staff were really nice and humble. Good experience overall.
Feedback - the food is overpriced! We loved the cocktails but the quantity of the food looking at the prices was below average. It’s like 4 small shrimps @1800. It was incredibly small portion like tasting menu instead of food on a plate. I hope they improve it over time as they got a really good ambiance, smooth jazz music, an amazing vibe. Food is where they really need to focus on. I don’t remember the pricing of cocktails but I am pretty confident everything was overpriced from my experience. At the end of the it’s Goa - unnecessary overpriced.

Kiki-By the Sea in Goa is an amazing spot right by the ocean. The view is breathtaking, and the vibe is super cozy and welcoming. They have a great mix of dishes from around the world, with fresh seafood being a standout. Their cocktails are also really tasty. The staff is super friendly and always ready to help. Whether you're on a date, with family, or hanging out with friends, it's a fantastic place to enjoy a meal. Definitely check it out!

A beautiful place to spend the entire afternoon till the evening. The sunsets are just beautiful from this place with a lot of sea side tables. The cocktails are  amazing and well made with plenty of in-house options to choose from. The food is their crow jewel, with an ample amount of options and decent portion sizes. We were very happy with the service and how warm the staff is, especially Arup, who hosted us and deserves a special mention in this review. If you're in Goa and want delicious food with an amazing ambience, it's a must to visit Kiki- By the sea.

description:
### Kiki - By the Sea: A Coastal Hideaway in Siolim

Nestled in the scenic surroundings of Siolim, Goa, **Kiki - By the Sea** welcomes diners with an impressive rating of **4.2** out of **3449** reviews. This beloved eatery has carved out a niche for itself in the culinary landscape with appealing tags that highlight its strengths: **cover charge** (156), **cocktails** (105), **sunset** (74), and **shravan** (43). Visitors often praise its fabulous blend of delightful cocktails and stunning views of the coastline, making it a prime destination for both relaxation and indulgence.

### Ambiance & Design

Kiki offers a soothing and inviting atmosphere, characterized by soft lighting and laid-back décor that effortlessly blends with its stunning coastal backdrop. Patrons can enjoy the warm gusts of breeze from the backwaters, contributing to the restaurant’s pleasant vibe. Featuring seaside tables that eagerly face the horizon, the venue is perfect for those wanting to catch a breathtaking sunset—an experience frequently mentioned in customer feedback. The soft jazz music layering the background further enhances the ambiance, making it an ideal spot for families, couples, or friend groups looking to unwind together.

![Kiki - By the Sea Ambiance](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdkS7Nfsds9-3stD01roRa9dj0ZDbLDQedUnh_UdDYDomz6RfzL14GNX03xt8BcLJEgqamI-KlOZA74flo86zqrzLgPhZIteUc5wWvpe72TuOF1QzurGR6Yc5uSzDpLIlHu3yLeFQQ=w375-h281-p)

### Menu & Culinary Experience

The menu at Kiki is an enticing tapestry of global cuisine, with a particular emphasis on **fresh seafood**. Diners have celebrated the culinary offerings as a highlight of their experience, often labeling it the "crown jewel" of the restaurant. Cocktails are another area of expertise, boasting a variety of in-house options that patrons rave about for their taste and presentation. However, some guests noted that while the flavor is commendable, portion sizes can be worryingly small compared to the pricing, suggesting that the kitchen may need to recalibrate its approach to value. Many have enjoyed the diverse assortment on the menu, ensuring there’s something for everyone.

![Delicious Cocktails](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdm4nRSelUUB6xM2UFmWN0PW79Hy6iHPId6hGQEOlwfZQiXKzY4am4usO44hvFjvQhxHbeDoClAm7-0v_AiGNPQm796NBDF_B4Nt4B-HJHVTMv01847crvEBRbokCganfJr7PPCawg=w375-h281-p)

### Customer Experience & Service

Customer service at Kiki does not go unnoticed, with many reviews highlighting the attentive and warm demeanor of the staff. Specific shoutouts were given to team members, such as Arup, who made diners feel particularly welcome. Reviews suggest a keen willingness on the part of the staff to assist, enhancing the overall dining experience. However, as indicated by some customers, expectations around food pricing and portion sizes remain a crucial area for improvement. Reservations are recommended, particularly during peak times, to ensure a seamless experience.

![Beautiful Sunset View](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdmyMGnxkzLfuGaAo0gD7cBsCG632nsqqJW-YUcX67YmP4noFmUH1BJuNjrxgvrNDuWoZX2gQ_sNfkxVmxzgXMGvOkGrrsQ-nNu71ezn5osKS2LU0mJdryQvtWyu7bvAN3uDccE-=w375-h281-p)

### Popularity & Reviews

Kiki - By the Sea has cultivated a loyal following, with diners consistently praising its charm and atmosphere on social media. While the general sentiment leans favorable, particularly about the cocktails and views, there are whispers of concern regarding food pricing that could deter future visits unless addressed. Nevertheless, the overall consensus is that Kiki is a must-visit for anyone looking to enjoy a meal with striking views and an inviting ambiance.

![Charming Coastal Dining](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdnDk9WCTD-hJgrVV31H2uXrSHoE1oyY6Wu451uzxv6tGV9xrFF4L-wKFLUQqEmC6Mf6tcUBXNrn1co71SMTJiwtp2qdejBuqY_2KyxR9LGtab2fv5MPzgbRL21fPlx3knA_sVyZpQ=w375-h281-p)

### Conclusion

In conclusion, **Kiki - By the Sea** offers a delightful blend of beautiful views, tasty cocktails, and a cozy atmosphere, making it a viable choice for your next outing. However, should the culinary offerings and pricing adjust to meet diners' expectations, this establishment may soon find itself at the forefront of Goa's dining scene, truly living up to its potential as a coastal gem. Whether you're there for a sunset cocktail or a meal with family or friends, Kiki is sure to leave a memorable mark on your Goa experience.
